Title: Software Engineering & Technology Lead
Company Location: Vienna, VA 22180, United States
Company Description:
Our work benefits the community through the acceleration of the development of electronics and embedded systems, making it easier to create technology that was previously not able to produce without an enormous budget. We hope our work with ensure our community has the platform it needs to develop new innovative technologies in domains like healthcare, agriculture, green energy, ultimately creating a better world for everyone.
At OpenQQuantify, we are building open-source projects in Generative AI for Electronics, Integrated Software Pipelines, and Embedded Systems to empower the community. Our mission is to enable users to explore new frontiers in technology by accelerating quantum development and pushing the boundaries of innovation. By teaching machines to think and solve problems, we provide the tools for creating simulations and designing optimized systems using data from the quantum world, including material specifications, hardware, physics, chemistry, and logic. We're committed to making these advanced technologies accessible so that everyone can achieve incredible breakthroughs and do truly amazing things.

Company Location: Vienna, VA 22180, United States
Company Description:
Our work benefits the community through the acceleration of the development of electronics and embedded systems, making it easier to create technology that was previously not able to produce without an enormous budget. We hope our work with ensure our community has the platform it needs to develop new innovative technologies in domains like healthcare, agriculture, green energy, ultimately creating a better world for everyone.
At OpenQQuantify, we are building open-source projects in Generative AI for Electronics, Integrated Software Pipelines, and Embedded Systems to empower the community. We're committed to making these advanced technologies accessible so that everyone can achieve incredible breakthroughs and do truly amazing things.

Title: Technical Lead
Company Location: 17 Gay Street, West Chester, PA 19380, United States
Company Description:
What if we could take the search out of job search? This is the question
Lensa has been answering since launching in San Francisco, California in
August 2016. Using machine learning, we instantly provide companies with
candidates and match professionals with positions that fit their skills,
goals, personalities, and needs.
How does it work? Lensa applies complex algorithms that identify the
skills needed to succeed on a given job. Candidates can play computer
games that assess their work style, thus gaining insight into their strengths
while unlocking career opportunities.
The result: job search that puts people first while reducing the time and
cost of talent acquisition.
Lensa passed 10 million job seeker registrations in 2019, making the com-
pany one of the premier career platforms.
With teams in multiple U.S. locations and a 60-strong crew of developers
and data scientists at its R & D headquarters in Europe, Lensa is working
every day to share its transformative career technology with the world.

Title: CEO/CTO EasyTpe By Kodeva Solutions digitales simplifiées pour les entreprises
Company Location: 16 Rue Des Tisserands, Montauban-De-Bretagne, Brittany 35360, France
Company Description:
Basée près de Rennes, Kodeva accompagne les TPE et PME dans leur transformation numérique grâce à des solutions informatiques sur mesure et des logiciels de gestion adaptés. 
Notre mission est d’optimiser la productivité, la sécurité des données et la gestion des processus de nos clients.
Notre proximité géographique nous permet de développer des solutions personnalisées en lien direct avec les besoins spécifiques de chaque entreprise, favorisant ainsi une collaboration de confiance et des résultats concrets.
Nous avons développé deux logiciels clés pour répondre aux besoins essentiels des entreprises : un outil de gestion du temps pour le suivi des projets et un logiciel de gestion de stock qui optimise les inventaires et la chaîne d’approvisionnement. Ces outils, automatisent les tâches administratives. 
En complément, nous offrons une expertise en développement d’applications sans compétences en développements (NoCode et LowCode) pour créer des solutions sur mesure, rapidement et efficacement.

Title: DevOps Tech Lead
Company Location: 17 Gay Street, West Chester, PA 19380, United States
Company Description:
What if we could take the search out of job search? This is the question
Lensa has been answering since launching in San Francisco, California in
August 2016. Using machine learning, we instantly provide companies with
candidates and match professionals with positions that fit their skills,
goals, personalities, and needs.
How does it work? Lensa applies complex algorithms that identify the
skills needed to succeed on a given job. Candidates can play computer
games that assess their work style, thus gaining insight into their strengths
while unlocking career opportunities.
The result: job search that puts people first while reducing the time and
cost of talent acquisition.
Lensa passed 10 million job seeker registrations in 2019, making the com-
pany one of the premier career platforms.
With teams in multiple U.S. locations and a 60-strong crew of developers
and data scientists at its R & D headquarters in Europe, Lensa is working
every day to share its transformative career technology with the world.

Company Location: 605 Castro Street, Mountain View, CA 94041, United States
Company Description:
The vast majority of human knowledge is still not on the internet. Most of it is trapped in the form of experience in people’s heads, or buried in books and papers that only experts can access. Our mission is to share and grow the world's knowledge, and we're building a world-class team to help us achieve this mission.
To do so, we have two knowledge sharing products:
Quora: a global knowledge sharing platform with over 400M monthly unique visitors, bringing people together to share insights on various topics and providing a unique platform to learn and connect with others.
Poe: a platform providing millions of global users with one place to chat, explore and build with a wide variety of AI language models (bots), including GPT-4, Claude 3, Gemini Pro, DALL-E 3 and more. As AI capabilities rapidly advance, Poe provides a single platform to instantly integrate and utilize these new models.

Title: Director, Platform Engineering
Company Location: 303 2nd Street, San Francisco, CA 94107, United States
Company Description:
At Scale, our mission is to accelerate the development of AI applications. We believe that to make the best models, you need the best data. 
The Scale Generative AI Platform leverages your enterprise data to customize powerful base generative models to safely unlock the value of AI. The Scale Data Engine consists of all the tools and features you need to collect, curate and annotate high-quality data, in addition to robust tools to evaluate and optimize your models. Scale powers the most advanced LLMs and generative models in the world through world-class RLHF, data generation, model evaluation, safety, and alignment.
Scale is trusted by leading technology companies like Microsoft and Meta, enterprises like Fox and Accenture, Generative AI companies like Open AI and Cohere, U.S. Government Agencies like the U.S. Army and the U.S. Airforce, and Startups like Brex and OpenSea.
